China’s ZTE Corp Said to Hire Lender for Arranging $500 Million in Loans

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-05-04T04:29:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-04/china-s-zte-corp-said-to-hire-lender-for-arranging-500-million-in-loans.html
ZTE Corp. (000063) , China’s second-largest
maker of phone equipment, is seeking $500 million in loans,
according to a person familiar with the matter.  Bank of China (Hong Kong) Ltd. is arranging the facility,
said the person, who asked not to be identified because the
details are private.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bloomberg News in Beijing at 
 hsanderson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
